  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK812">
<l>uṟiṉaṭ ṭaṟiṉoorūu moppilār kēṇmai </l>
<l>peṟiṉu miḻappiṉu meṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of what avail is it to get or lose the friendship of those who love when there is gain and leave when there is none ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
